00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:59,520
I can investigate further if you wish,
but you've gotta realize

237
00:15:59,520 --> 00:16:02,550
it's a case about one individual
and it happened overseas.

238
00:16:02,790 --> 00:16:05,550
No, this is more than enough
for a great story.

239
00:16:06,260 --> 00:16:08,890
I'd rather have you investigate
the whereabouts of Nana's mother.

240
00:16:10,060 --> 00:16:11,030
Thank you as usual.

241
00:16:11,830 --> 00:16:15,730
But unless BLAST becomes big,
won't this go to waste?

242
00:16:16,000 --> 00:16:19,170
Just watch. There's no doubt about it.
They'll be big.

243
00:16:19,470 --> 00:16:21,870
But it appears that Gaia has
no intention of letting them debut.

244
00:16:22,210 --> 00:16:23,870
I'll make it happen.

245
00:16:24,450 --> 00:16:26,070
Even if they were to debut,
they won't sell.

246
00:16:26,680 --> 00:16:29,080
A visually attractive band
may attract fad followers,

247
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:30,640
but that will repel the real music lovers.

248
00:16:31,120 --> 00:16:33,880
- And, these songs aren't what...
- Stop talking like some music critic!

249
00:16:34,250 --> 00:16:37,020
What the people want never changes!

250
00:16:37,260 --> 00:16:38,780
They want a stimulating topic!

251
00:16:39,130 --> 00:16:40,660
And yet the young brats of today
just don't get it.

252
00:16:40,660 --> 00:16:44,500
They all believe they're some great artist,
it makes me sick.

253
00:16:45,370 --> 00:16:49,890
A world where "honor student" bands
like Trapnest reign is as sleepy as hell!

254
00:16:51,140 --> 00:16:53,370
I would just love to break that nose of
Takumi that he proudly sticks up high.

255
00:16:54,910 --> 00:16:57,500
Anyway, I look forward
to tomorrow's party.

256
00:16:58,110 --> 00:16:59,510
We'll open everyone's eyes.

257
00:16:59,680 --> 00:17:01,880
Huh? But "Search" isn't on the shelves
until the day after tomorrow, right?

258
00:17:02,150 --> 00:17:04,380
I sold half of the information
to TV networks.

259
00:17:04,550 --> 00:17:08,090
They were really into my scenario
and practically handed over their wallets.

260
00:17:08,090 --> 00:17:10,060
It wasn't about getting a scoop, huh?

261
00:17:10,120 --> 00:17:12,850
My objective is to increase
magazine sales!

262
00:17:13,130 --> 00:17:16,130
Get the people excited with news
about their love affair,

263
00:17:16,130 --> 00:17:18,370
and the people will jump
at the precious photo!

264
00:17:18,370 --> 00:17:20,390
You got a picture of them together?

265
00:17:22,670 --> 00:17:24,030
It looks great.

266
00:17:26,310 --> 00:17:32,780
That day, I waited for Hachi in front
of her place until sunset,

267
00:17:32,780 --> 00:17:34,410
but I couldn't see her.

268
00:17:36,150 --> 00:17:39,180
I'll come again tomorrow after work.

269
00:17:40,150 --> 00:17:42,350
I have a little time before
I go to the studio.

270
00:17:42,760 --> 00:17:45,060
I'll get her phone number from Yasu,

271
00:17:45,060 --> 00:17:46,750
so we don't miss each other
like this again.

272
00:17:47,800 --> 00:17:50,360
It's not like I'll never see her again.

273
00:17:51,730 --> 00:17:52,700
There's always tomorrow.

274
00:17:54,230 --> 00:17:56,100
Sorry to keep you for so long.

275
00:17:56,670 --> 00:17:58,570
I'm so glad we got the chance to
talk about all kinds of stuff.

276
00:17:58,940 --> 00:18:01,910
Housewives are craving for
the chance to talk to people.

277
00:18:02,380 --> 00:18:05,000
Don't remain at home thinking only
about the baby in your tummy.

278
00:18:05,350 --> 00:18:07,370
You need to get in touch with
the outside world.

279
00:18:07,980 --> 00:18:12,940
But the only plans I have to go out
are shopping and checkups.

280
00:18:13,220 --> 00:18:14,520
Why don't you take lessons
on something?

281
00:18:14,760 --> 00:18:15,980
You'd also make housewife friends
that way.

282
00:18:16,060 --> 00:18:17,020
Great idea.

283
00:18:17,360 --> 00:18:19,380
Good luck with your practice, Shin.

284
00:18:20,130 --> 00:18:22,260
Personally, I think some things
are impossible to achieve,

285
00:18:22,260 --> 00:18:23,560
no matter how much you practice.

286
00:18:23,830 --> 00:18:24,960
That's not true!

287
00:18:25,200 --> 00:18:28,460
I believe that BLAST will become
the best band in Japan someday!

288
00:18:31,540 --> 00:18:35,300
Well then, Madam, we'll meet again
when your husband's not around.

289
00:18:35,540 --> 00:18:36,510
Yes.

290
00:18:52,760 --> 00:18:53,730
Shin!

291
00:19:03,440 --> 00:19:04,900
How is Nobu?

292
00:19:11,850 --> 00:19:15,680
He keeps playing his guitar!
It's so noisy I can't get any sleep!

293
00:19:23,420 --> 00:19:25,150
I can't wait until dawn.

294
00:19:26,790 --> 00:19:28,660
I hope it'll be sunny tomorrow.

295
00:19:36,240 --> 00:19:37,400
Ouch!

296
00:19:37,500 --> 00:19:38,940
Oh, sorry. You're home.

297
00:19:45,350 --> 00:19:46,640
Seven o'clock?

298
00:19:46,810 --> 00:19:50,610
He just got to bed. I'm amazed how
he can get up and go to work.

299
00:20:07,370 --> 00:20:10,230
What are you watching a video
of yourself so early in the morning?

300
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:13,870
No. We're on TV.

301
00:20:14,040 --> 00:20:15,010
Oh, how nice.

302
00:20:15,180 --> 00:20:16,230
Is this "Channel Nana"?

