311
00:20:29,960 --> 00:20:33,720
a band on the brink of
a major debut with Gaia Records.

312
00:20:33,890 --> 00:20:34,860
Her name, Nana!

313
00:20:41,600 --> 00:20:44,040
Ever since that day when
the thick clouds passed

314
00:20:44,040 --> 00:20:46,470
and I was suddenly in the spotlight...

315
00:20:48,040 --> 00:20:53,210
The place we were standing was
not a stage, but the center of a ring.

316
00:20:57,550 --> 00:21:01,990
I can still hear the cheers and
jeers ringing in my head.

317
00:21:03,320 --> 00:21:04,310
Loud and annoying.

318
00:21:08,030 --> 00:21:13,930
I can't count
how many nights

319
00:21:14,000 --> 00:21:18,700
I wished tomorrow
would never come

320
00:21:18,770 --> 00:21:25,470
To live as I am
without being fake

321
00:21:25,550 --> 00:21:29,070
What do I need

322
