If I don't believe in myself,
what can I believe in

323
00:21:37,290 --> 00:21:42,390
The answer is
too close to see

324
00:21:42,460 --> 00:21:48,630
Black tears are
falling down

325
00:21:48,700 --> 00:21:55,570
I have nothing,
only sadness

326
00:21:55,640 --> 00:22:00,670
I can't put it
into words

327
00:22:00,750 --> 00:22:06,740
My whole body
starts to ache

328
00:22:06,820 --> 00:22:12,160
I can't stand it anymore
on my own

